{"tid":1970383,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《絕命大平台》最小200層地獄 上面既人食盡所有美食 下層屎都無得食","createTime":"2020-04-13T06:09:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T07:22:48.000Z","uid":69309,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"99d413186012ed847a5184b772e1eb2f06604806","tid":1970383,"uid":69309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T06:09:30.000Z","msg":"《絕命大平台》擁有一個奇幻又恐怖的設定，上百人被關在一個有升降平台的百層監獄中，每天機關都會從第一層開始傳送一整桌的美味食物，讓每一層的兩個囚犯在固定的時間內可以上前大吃，吃完之後那一桌就直接往下降給更低階的囚犯，因此上層的人越暴食，下層的人就越飢餓，並只能吃那些難以入口的廚餘，導演 Galder Gaztelu-Urrutia 用這個絕妙的奇想機關來諷刺社會階級。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.juksy.com/files/articles/98862/800x_100_w-5e6850faf3f9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F98862%2F800x_100_w-5e6850faf3f9f.jpg&h=3e5a5eb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.juksy.com/files/articles/98862/800x_100_w-5e6850fa84f44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F98862%2F800x_100_w-5e6850fa84f44.jpg&h=2467d1ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-HtKZLdhxYw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-HtKZLdhxYw&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWRPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=33a1b1c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-HtKZLdhxYw</a><br />\n暫時得呢到有得睇 雖然殘體 但無辦法 其他網死哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f54f5062983f6044044ed1be2feeddb2437e85a0","tid":1970383,"uid":307329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T06:12:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c45beaf069cfe49b2957ae6b2b5e529669850bcd","tid":1970383,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f54f5062983f6044044ed1be2feeddb2437e85a0","tid":1970383,"uid":307329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T06:12:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T06:17:03.000Z","msg":"最後係就算安排得好，資源都係有限係分配唔到落去，佢地本身想2百